TextChange: Plagiorism is a major issue in our learning institutions today. It is very easy for people to cheat becuase there are so many available resources for people to get information. Such as, the internet. It is something that needs to be dealt with becuase it is not fair that people can turn in work that is not their own. It shows that people do not take the time to learn for themselves.\n\nWhen I was in high school there were several students that would try to have others do their work for them becaused they didn't have time or the interest in the subject. They would offer to pay for other students to complete their work and they in turn would turn in the work as their own. The students got caught and were given Fs in the class and were not allowed to graduate with the rest of their class.
